48.3. Let $a_{1}, a_{2}, a_{3}, \ldots, a_{n}$ be given natural numbers. Consider $n$ numbers:

$$
\begin{array}{r}
a_{1} \\
a_{1}+a_{2} \\
a_{1}+a_{2}+a_{3} \\
a_{1}+a_{2}+\ldots+a_{n}
\end{array}
